column2: select top # eid,Eye_problems_disorders_#,c.meaning  from dbo.Eyesight a       cross apply openjson(Eye_problems_disorders_#) j      cross apply openjson(j.value) v join metadata.columninfo m on m.column_name=&&& join metadata.encoding c on c.value=v.value AND     m.encoding_id=c.encoding_id where v.value=#
